# Phase 1: Foundation — Implementation Plan

Build the end-to-end core loop: **paste notes → LLM extracts proposals (with tool-calling for real project IDs) → user approves → tasks created in Vikunja**. Single DuckDB file for all data (users + proposals). Backend is FastAPI with full auth ported from archive. Frontend is fresh Svelte 5 + Tailwind CSS.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Vikunja must be running** before backend integration works. Step 1 sets up Docker Compose, but you'll need to manually create projects and generate an API token in the Vikunja UI before testing.

> [!NOTE]
> **Ollama/confidential mode is deferred to Phase 2.** Phase 1 uses Gemini API only. The `confidential` toggle will be visible in the UI but disabled with a "Coming in Phase 2" tooltip.

---

