### Docker / Infrastructure

#### [NEW] [docker-compose.yml](file:///data/epicrunze/Projects/cognito/docker-compose.yml)
- Vikunja service (port 3456), Agent backend (port 8000), Agent frontend (port 5173 → nginx)
- Volume mount for Vikunja data + single DuckDB file (`./data/agent.duckdb`)
- `extra_hosts` for future Linux Docker → host Ollama access

