- Python ≥3.10, `uv`-managed
- Deps: `fastapi`, `uvicorn[standard]`, `httpx`, `pydantic-settings`, `python-jose[cryptography]`, `python-multipart`, `email-validator`, `duckdb`, `sse-starlette`

#### [NEW] [backend/app/config.py](file:///data/epicrunze/Projects/cognito/backend/app/config.py)
