- `init_schema()` creates all 4 tables in one place: `users` (from archive), `task_proposals`, `vikunja_projects`, `agent_config` (spec §3.4 — translated to DuckDB DDL with `gen_random_uuid()` and DuckDB JSON/BOOLEAN types)

